member.name: WS_UNKNOWN_ENDPOINT_IDENTITY
member.summary: Type for unknown endpoint identity. This type is only used to represent an endpoint identity type that was deserialized but was not understood.

member.name: WS_UNKNOWN_ENDPOINT_IDENTITY.identity
member.summary: The base type from which this type and all other endpoint identity types derive.

member.name: WS_UNKNOWN_ENDPOINT_IDENTITY.element
member.summary: An XML buffer containing a single XML Element which corresponds to the identity element that was not understood. This field may not be NULL.
